results.abstract: training of 7 Mercury Astronauts, Langley base, described; illus
results.snippet: OF the seven young men who are at present in training to be the free world's first men into outer space, a flight surgeon who is perhaps closer to them as a group than any other individual said recently: "The only thing about them is that they're...
results.lead_paragraph: OF the seven young men who are at present in training to be the free world's first men into outer space, a flight surgeon who is perhaps closer to them as a group than any other individual said recently: "The only thing about them is that they're sort of supernormal." After a couple of days spent watching them at work and at ease, the phrase seems entirely apt.
